snippet.title: Indie shoot'm up project 2016 - remaking the first level - No title yet
snippet.description:
Another video from my new indie Shoot'm up project.
Don't mind the low video quality and the slow downs, it's just my recording software and my PC can't handle recording in full HD.

No the first level remake is almost done, 2nd level is already finished.

Graphics, sound effects and coding by me.

Music from Blazing star by SNK.

I'm still looking for a sound artist for the bgd music.
